        .process__panel(data-order='1')
          h3.h3.process__panel-header Direct to Business
          p.process__panel-content Content strategy and creative treatments for teams who build their brands in house, but sometimes need to bring in the experts to get more done.

        .process__panel(data-order='3')
          h3.h3.process__panel-header Non-Profit World
          p.process__panel-content We help the world’s do-gooders do good, working within the constraints of the public sector to tell the world’s most heartfelt and compelling stories.

